    • Moves

      public Moves​(Builder builder1, java.util.ArrayList<Square> moves1, Builder builder2, java.util.ArrayList<Square> moves2, boolean isDome, boolean female)
      class used to comunicate to the client all the available moves of the actual phase.
      Parameters:
      builder1 - is the first builder.
      moves1 - all the places where the first builder can move or build.
      builder2 - is the second builder.
      moves2 - all the places where the second builder can move or build.
      isDome - boolean that indicates if the player can build a dome thanks to a god power.
      female - to indicate that the female worker has a special effect.
